HEADWORD: Unequivocal
<hw>Un`e*quiv"o*cal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not equivocal;
not doubtful; not ambiguous; evident; sincere; plain; <as>as,
<ex>unequivocal</ex> evidence; <ex>unequivocal</ex> words.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un`e*quiv"o*cal*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un`e*quiv"o*cal*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

